WEBVTT

00:00:00.720 --> 00:00:05.520
In the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, amen.

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:11.160
The reading from the Sinek Sadion from A3rd, on which we commemorate, the Holy Martyrs

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:18.760
Timothy and Mauta, St. Timothy came from a village near Thebes in Egypt.

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:23.900
He was ordained reader, and through the reading of the lives of the saints, during church

00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:30.260
services, he confirmed the Christians in their hope of good things to come.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:37.340
When Diocletians first edicts against the Christians were published in 304, only 20 days after his

00:00:37.340 --> 00:00:44.140
marriage to the devout Mauta, Timothy was denounced as an ardent preacher of the new religion

00:00:44.140 --> 00:00:51.060
and taken before Aryan, the prefect of Thebes, who called on him to hand over the service

00:00:51.060 --> 00:00:52.060
books.

00:00:52.060 --> 00:00:58.740
But the saint refused, saying, as a father could not possibly willingly give his children

00:00:58.740 --> 00:01:05.200
over to death, in the same way I would die rather than give over these books, by which

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:11.660
the faithful and I myself receive the grace of God and the protection of his angels to

00:01:11.660 --> 00:01:13.340
be burned.

00:01:13.340 --> 00:01:20.540
Beside himself with fury, Aryan had red-hot spikes thrust into his ears, piercing the

00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:24.580
eardrum, and gouged out his eyes.

00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:27.700
They both falling to the ground.

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:33.820
They then tied him to a nail-covered wheel and flayed his skin, but Timothy was healed

00:01:33.820 --> 00:01:39.620
by the grace of God and held out against the other tortures, crying out that nothing could

00:01:39.620 --> 00:01:43.700
separate him from the love of Christ.

00:01:43.700 --> 00:01:49.040
The tyrant then had him thrown in prison and summoned Mauta with the hope of using her

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:52.060
to overcome Timothy's resistance.

00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:57.280
He tried at first, through flattery, to induce her to bring her husband to reason so that she

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:01.880
would not lose him after only twenty days of marriage.

00:02:01.880 --> 00:02:07.960
After a short walk with Timothy, Mauta left the prison filled with a holy ardor and confessed

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:15.160
to the prefect that she also was a Christian and was ready to give her life for Christ.

00:02:15.160 --> 00:02:21.440
Aryan had her hair shorn, and after having had her fingers cut off, she was thrown into boiling

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:23.000
water.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:30.400
She, however, remained untouched, and said to the magistrate, your fire is a poor one.

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:35.760
If you haven't got enough wood, send servants to my parents' house, and they will give you

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.760
some.

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:43.280
Aryan went up to her, wanting to verify if the water was hot enough.

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:48.400
Mauta, through some of it at him, and yelling with pain the prefect saw the skin of his hand

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:51.000
peeling off with the scalding.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:57.680
He then ordered that the saint be burned with torches primed with pitch and sulfur.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:04.320
But Mauta still remained untouched, and mocked the powerlessness of her persecutors.

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:12.560
Aryan then ordered that the couple be tied to crosses facing each other, and left to die slowly.

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:20.400
They remained thus crucified in imitation of our Lord Jesus Christ for nine whole days,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:25.920
sustaining each other in patience.

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:30.960
Filled with rage at the spectacle of the victory of Christ who dwelt within them through faith,

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:37.080
the devil took human form and gave Mauta a cup of milk mixed with honey in order to refresh

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:42.120
her, but the saint repulsed him with her prayer.

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:49.680
He then carried her in imagination to a land of delights with the river of milk flowing nearby.

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:56.360
She armed herself with a holy anger in order to reject once again these deceptive advances,

00:03:56.360 --> 00:04:01.360
and declared that she preferred to drink the cup of eternal life that Christ presented to

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:04.520
her on the cross.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:09.120
As soon as the demon departed, an angel of the Lord appeared.

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:15.320
Took Mauta by the hand, and, leading her in a vision to heaven, showed her a resplendent

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:22.920
throne on which there lay a brightly shining robe and a golden crown, and he said to her,

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:28.320
it is for you that these things are prepared.

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:34.360
He then took her to a still higher place where there was another throne, another white robe,

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:40.840
and another crown, and added, these are prepared for your husband, as it was he who was the

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:44.520
cause of your salvation.

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:50.720
Come to herself once more, Mauta told Timothy of this revelation, and it was with joy that

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:57.080
they together confided their souls into God's keeping on the tenth day.

00:04:57.080 --> 00:05:02.760
Devout Christians bought their bodies with silver and buried them with honor, giving thanks

00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:06.960
to God for having glorified His holy martyrs.

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:13.240
Many healings were later wrought, not only over their relics, but also for the faithful

00:05:13.240 --> 00:05:20.640
who venerated their icon or called on the names of the Holy Spouses.

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:26.840
Through the prayers of our Holy Father's, O Lord Jesus Christ our God, have mercy on us

00:05:26.840 --> 00:05:27.840
and save us.
